high_descs: Turn to the end of the table, on your left.
Pick up the brown cup and spoon, to the left of the wine bottle on the white table.
Turn to your left and go to the sink to the left of the refrigerator.
Place the brown cup and spoon in the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a brown cup and spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the table.
Pick up the orange cup that's in front of you so the spoon magically hangs off the bottom of it.
Turn left and walk to the counter then take a big step to your right.
Put the orange cup in the sink below and to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup in the sink.

high_descs: Move forward to the wall, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the cup on the table.
Turn left, go forward, turn right to go around the table, then turn left to approach the sink.
Put the cup in the sink, next to the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup in the sink.
